name: "🐱 Nuzzle Wall | Cat Blessing"
description: "Share your cat photo and blessing with NuzzleMate."
title: "🐾 [Cat Blessing] "
labels: ["cat-blessing", "community", "nuzzle-wall"]
body:
  - type: markdown
    attributes:
      value: |
        Thank you for joining the **Nuzzle Wall** 🐱✨

        Share a photo of your cat and write a small blessing for NuzzleMate.
        Your submission will be publicly visible in this repository's Issues.

        感谢你加入 **贴贴祝福墙** 🐾  
        你可以上传自己的小猫照片，并为 NuzzleMate 写下一句祝福。  
        请注意：提交内容会公开显示在本仓库的 Issues 中。

  - type: input
    id: cat_name
    attributes:
      label: "Cat's name | 小猫名字"
      description: "What is your cat's name?"
      placeholder: "e.g. Momo / 奶黄 / 芝士 / 小金豆"
    validations:
      required: false

  - type: dropdown
    id: cat_type
    attributes:
      label: "Cat type | 小猫类型"
      description: "Choose the type that best describes your cat."
      options:
        - British Shorthair Golden | 金渐层
        - British Shorthair Silver | 银渐层
        - Ragdoll | 布偶
        - Domestic Shorthair | 中华田园猫
        - Maine Coon | 缅因
        - Persian | 波斯
        - Siamese | 暹罗
        - Other | 其他
    validations:
      required: false

  - type: textarea
    id: cat_photo
    attributes:
      label: "Cat photo | 小猫照片"
      description: "Drag and drop your cat photo here, or paste an image link. You can also use Markdown image syntax."
      placeholder: |
        Drag and drop your cat photo here.
        你可以把小猫照片直接拖到这个输入框里。
    validations:
      required: true

  - type: textarea
    id: blessing
    attributes:
      label: "Blessing for NuzzleMate | 给 NuzzleMate 的祝福"
      description: "Write a short blessing, wish, or message."
      placeholder: |
        May every pet be healthy, loved, and gently protected.
        愿每一只小猫小狗都被温柔守护，健康长大。
    validations:
      required: true

  - type: textarea
    id: story
    attributes:
      label: "A little story | 我和小猫的小故事"
      description: "Optional. Tell us a small story about your cat."
      placeholder: |
        She loves sleeping beside my laptop while I code.
        她喜欢在我写代码的时候趴在电脑旁边睡觉。
    validations:
      required: false

  - type: checkboxes
    id: consent
    attributes:
      label: "Consent | 公开展示确认"
      description: "Please confirm before submitting."
      options:
        - label: "I confirm that I have the right to share this photo, and I understand that this submission will be public."
          required: true
        - label: "我确认我有权分享这张照片，并理解该内容会公开展示在 GitHub Issues 中。"
          required: true
